{"tid":1460830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三縣長赴國台辦爭取自由行 總統：請陸委會了解是否報備","createTime":"2019-08-13T05:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T09:50:17.000Z","uid":58335,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"efce2aec1ed56f558398c3722f3472e874981847","tid":1460830,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:02:32.000Z","msg":"屌奶星<br />\n台灣真係好撚多賣台賊<br />\n華人就是多漢奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔記者賴筱桐／新北報導〕中國日前公告暫停47個城市人民赴台自由行政策，金門縣長楊鎮浯、連江縣長劉增應與澎湖縣長賴峰偉，今天前往中國北京拜訪國台辦，盼爭取中國的對台旅遊政策，對3座離島有所區隔。蔡英文總統今天表示，將請陸委會了解3位首長是否報備。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文今天視察捷運萬大線二期工程，被問到離島3位縣市首長前往國台辦，蔡英文表示，中國限制觀光客自由行，政府已多次表達立場，自由行對很多中國年輕旅客來說，是認識台灣很好的機會，中國為了種種原因取消，確實很遺憾，對中國也是一項損失，中國人民無法到台灣來，親身體驗台灣的風土民情，對兩岸交流不是一件好事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於3位首長赴國台辦是否恰當？蔡英文說，這屬於中央事務，將請陸委會了解出發之前，3位首長是否報備，以及事後是否報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2881895\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2881895&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y9%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=498e4fa3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2881895</a>"},{"pid":"540cd53c0e5b4c27c0105e86d42b786c6ed28a85","tid":1460830,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc14067a5fea1e77e610bc9299b5595329ec252","tid":1460830,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:49:18.000Z","msg":"屌 呢幾個島割讓畀支那算啦"},{"pid":"5ae065e46186f35c0fb7951856cdfeee95154092","tid":1460830,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbc14067a5fea1e77e610bc9299b5595329ec252","tid":1460830,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:49:18.000Z","msg":"屌 呢幾個島割讓畀支那算啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:50:17.000Z","msg":"冇左緩衝帶唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}